oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Salem Associate Reformed Presbyterian Church
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Salem Associate Reformed Presbyterian Church, Atoka. The cemetery is shown next to the building.
Salem Presbyterian Church was organized June 19, 1836. The sanctuary is the 4th one to be built on the premises, the 1st being a log church and the 3rd having burned to the ground in 1939.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
